$ Registry: HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Policies\Google\Chrome

At least two subkeys:
  • → Windows/registry/tree/HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE/Software/Policies/Google/Chrome/ExtensionInstallBlacklist[`ExtensionInstallBlacklist`] (to specify Chome extensions that must not be installed)
  • → Windows/registry/tree/HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE/Software/Policies/Google/Chrome/ExtensioninstallWhitelist[`ExtensioninstallWhitelist`] (to override the black list with extensions that may be installed)
